  Home  Insider Trading  Insider Trading Activity Shiloh Industries, Inc. (NASDAQ:SHLO) – Major Shareholder Sold 500,000...     Insider Trading  Insider Trading Activity Shiloh Industries, Inc. (NASDAQ:SHLO) – Major Shareholder Sold 500,000 shares of Stock  ByME Staff -July 20, 2017 0  Share on Facebook
Tweet on Twitter


 Insider Trading Activity For Shiloh Industries, Inc. (NASDAQ:SHLO)
Mtd Holdings Inc , Major Shareholder of Shiloh Industries, Inc. (NASDAQ:SHLO) reportedly Sold 500,000 shares of the company’s stock at an average price of 7.76 for a total transaction amount of $3,880,000.00 SEC Form
Insider Trading History For Shiloh Industries, Inc. (NASDAQ:SHLO)
On 10/3/2013 Michael P Randall, Insider, sold 2,000 with an average share price of $13.00 per share and the total transaction amounting to $26,000.00.View SEC Filing
On 10/11/2013 Michael P Randall, Insider, sold 1,000 with an average share price of $13.65 per share and the total transaction amounting to $13,650.00.View SEC Filing
On 4/2/2014 Anthony M Parente, VP, sold 10,000 with an average share price of $18.59 per share and the total transaction amounting to $185,900.00.View SEC Filing
On 7/1/2015 Curtis Moll, Director, bought 15,400 with an average share price of $12.95 per share and the total transaction amounting to $199,430.00.View SEC Filing
On 7/16/2015 Dieter Kaesgan, Director, bought 111 with an average share price of $12.50 per share and the total transaction amounting to $1,387.50.View SEC Filing
On 9/16/2015 Ramzi Hermiz, CEO, bought 11,600 with an average share price of $8.60 per share and the total transaction amounting to $99,760.00.View SEC Filing
On 7/19/2017 Mtd Holdings Inc, Major Shareholder, sold 500,000 with an average share price of $7.76 per share and the total transaction amounting to $3,880,000.00.View SEC Filing
Analyst Ratings For Shiloh Industries, Inc. (NASDAQ:SHLO)These are No ratings tracked in the last 12 months. .The current consensus rating for Shiloh Industries, Inc. (NASDAQ:SHLO) is N/A (Score: NaN) with a consensus target price of N/A
Recent Trading Activity for Shiloh Industries, Inc. (NASDAQ:SHLO)Shares of Shiloh Industries, Inc. closed the previous trading session at 8.46 down -0.15 -1.74% with 331,679 shares trading hands. 
